OL,3,CFire breaks out for second time at
OL,4,Cderelict Hotel California
OL,6,FA derelict Cornish hotel named after
OL,7,Fthe Eagles hit, Hotel California, has
OL,8,Fgone up in smoke for the second time.
OL,10,FThe dilapidated hotel, in Pentire
OL,11,FCrescent, Newquay, was in flames on
OL,12,FSunday 20 October with fire crews from
OL,13,Ffive separate locations in attendance.
OL,15,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,16,Fscene of the fire at around 6pm. The
OL,17,Falarm was raised after smoke was seen
OL,18,Fat the rear of the old hotel.
