OL,3,CFire breaks out for second time at
OL,4,Cderelict Hotel California
OL,6,FFire crews from Newquay initially
OL,7,Fattended and confirmed the fire at the
OL,8,Fback of the building. A total of six
OL,9,Fcrews battled the fire at the derelict
OL,10,Fthree-storey building.
OL,12,FThe cause of the fire is not known at
OL,13,Fthis stage. It is not believed that
OL,14,Fanyone sustained any injuries during
OL,15,Fthe fire.
OL,17,FA statement from Cornwall Fire and
OL,18,FRescue Service said: "A 999 call was
OL,19,Freceived at 18:00 to a report of smoke
OL,20,Fcoming from the rear of a derelict
OL,21,Fhotel beside the Gannel River.
