OL,6,F"Two appliances from Newquay were
OL,7,Fmobilised and following their arrival,
OL,8,Fthey confirmed there was a fire in the
OL,9,Frear of the building.
OL,11,F"Two additional fire appliances from
OL,12,FSt Columb and St Dennis have been
OL,13,Fmobilised alongside support vehicles
OL,14,Ffrom Launceston and St Austell.
OL,16,F"Firefighters were using breathing
OL,17,Fapparatus and hose reels."
