OL,3,CFire breaks out for second time at
OL,4,Cderelict Hotel California
OL,6,FJust before 7pm, the fire service
OL,7,Fconfirmed the fire had been
OL,8,Fextinguished. It said: "@1852hrs the
OL,9,Ffire was declared as being
OL,10,Fextinguished and all appliances
OL,11,Freturned to their home stations."
OL,13,FIn June, a major fire broke out at the
OL,14,Fderelict Hotel California and
OL,15,Ffirefighters battled the blaze.
