OL,3,CFire breaks out for second time at
OL,4,Cderelict Hotel California
OL,6,FDue to the size of the fire, the roof
OL,7,Fof the building collapsed and the
OL,8,Fmissing floorboards inside the
OL,9,Fbuilding meant crews had no choice but
OL,10,Fto fight the fire from outside the
OL,11,Fhotel.
OL,13,FThe hotel closed in 2021 and was used
OL,14,Fby homeless people. After the hotel
OL,15,Fclosed at the end of 2021, a statement
OL,16,Fwas submitted with the planning
OL,17,Fapplication stating that "after years
OL,18,Fof steady decay the hotel grew
OL,19,Foutdated and in a state of disrepair".
