OL,3,CFire breaks out for second time at
OL,4,Cderelict Hotel California
OL,6,FBack in February, the Hotel California
OL,7,Fwas set to be demolished to make way
OL,8,Ffor a new development, after planning
OL,9,Fpermission was agreed by Cornwall
OL,10,FCouncil.
OL,12,FThe development was expected to see
OL,13,Fthe entire hotel complex replaced with
OL,14,Fa residential development which would
OL,15,Finclude a building with 20 apartments
OL,16,Fand four semi-detached houses.
